    <a name="about" href="#about" style="color: inherit;"><h2>1. About</h2></a>
    <p>By trade, I tell computers what to do. I make apps, I build products, I throw events. I think about people, urbanism, housing, the internet, and living a good life. I live in Toronto, and I prefer they/them pronouns.</p>
    <p>You can find me on <a href="https://hachyderm.io/@phillmv" rel="me">mastodon</a>, and on <a href="https://instagram.com/phillmv">instagram</a>. Reach me by email via phillmv at okayfail dot com.</p>
