  <a name="recent-writing" href="#recent-writing" style="color: inherit;"><h2>2. Selected Writing</h2></a>
  <p>You can find <a href="/archive.html">an archive of my writing here</a>. Follow along using <a href="/atom.xml">the rss feed</a>.</p>

